title: TruSonik High-Performance Swimming Pool Pump – 2HP 110V Pool Pump – 111GPM Pool Filter – Stainless Steel Motor Drive Shaft – Works with Inground and Above Ground Pools
features: HEAVY DUTY DESIGN – Featuring a heavy-duty corrosion proof polymer housing for the filter portion of the pump as well as a 304 stainless-steel drive shaft for the high-powered 2HP electric motor.

EASY INSTALLATION – Our swimming pool pump is not only heavy-duty, but also simple and easy to install as well. Including an in-depth installation manual, you’ll have your pool’s filtration system up and running in no time. Also, unlike other pool pumps that require special wiring, ours simply plugs into your home’s AC outlet.
FOR INGROUND & ABOVE GROUND POOLS – Unlike other swimming pool pumps that work either strictly for above or inground pools, ours works seamlessly for both.

LARGE FLOW RATE– With a flow rate of 111 gallons of water per minute, our TruSonik Swimming Pool Pump is designed to easily clean and filter pools of the most common sizes quickly and easily with a large filter basket that requires less emptying than other pumps.

FULL 1 YEAR MANUFACTURER WARRANTY - We are fully confident in the quality and durability of our products and back them with a full 1 year warranty. In the very unlikely event you encounter an issue with your purchase, simply call or email one of our friendly customer service experts and we will gladly take care of it.
description: TruSonik High-Powered and Heavy-Duty Swimming Pool Pump
Tired of going through pool pumps that promise high flow rates, but just aren’t able to deliver or stop working only after a few months of use?
Do you look for only the best in performance and reliability when purchasing your swimming pool’s necessary equipment?
Well, TruSonik has the perfect solution for you!

Featuring a high flow rate of 110 gallons of water per minute and housing a 2HP motor to help push all of that water makes the TruSonik Swimming Pool Pump one of the highest flowing and best performing pool pumps in its class. The ultra-efficient use of its motor ensures that you’ll be able to keep your pool clean and clear more easily throughout the spring and summer, and all year-round for indoor pools.

With its outstanding and remarkable construction, TruSonik’s Pool Pump will also work with both inground and above ground pools, so no matter the type of pool you have, you’re guaranteed, filtration, and reliability that competitors just can’t match. TruSonik’s Swimming Pool Pump has also been constructed to run cooler and be more energy efficient than other pool pumps and filtration systems on the market.
